    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-08-30T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-08-30T00:00:00-05:00" n="102"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d102">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">841.244/8–3044</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                            <gloss type="to">President</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-08-30">August 30,
                            1944</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p rend="center">
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Memorandum for the President</hi>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">Subject: Argentina</p>
                <p>I attach hereto a draft of telegram which I would suggest that you send to the
                    Prime Minister, if you agree.<note n="1" xml:id="d102fn1">Roosevelt sent the
                        suggested message to Churchill on August 31, 1944. See <hi rend="italic"
                            >infra</hi>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>C[<hi rend="smallcaps">ordell</hi>] H[<hi rend="smallcaps"
                        >ull</hi>]</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
